<!--
  DFW Automation Pipeline — ServiceNow Update Set
  Version: 2.0.0
  Scope: x_dfw (DFW Automation)

  This Update Set contains all ServiceNow components required for the DFW
  Automation Pipeline integration. Import via System Update Sets > Retrieved
  Update Sets > Import Update Set from XML.

  Components Included:
    - Service Catalog Items (5)
    - Catalog Client Scripts (6)
    - Server-Side Script Includes (2)
    - Business Rules (2)
    - UI Policies (conditional field policies)
    - Custom Table: x_dfw_rule_registry

  Prerequisites:
    - Enterprise Tag Dictionary table (u_enterprise_tag_dictionary) must exist
    - vRO REST Message must be configured
    - Mid Server must be available for outbound REST calls
-->
