  <!--
    Individual component records are omitted from this template.
    In a production deployment, this file is generated by the ServiceNow
    CI/CD pipeline from the source files in:
      - src/servicenow/catalog/client-scripts/
      - src/servicenow/catalog/server-scripts/
      - src/servicenow/catalog/ui-policies/
      - src/servicenow/business-rules/
      - src/servicenow/integration/

    To generate a complete Update Set:
      1. Deploy components to a ServiceNow sub-production instance
      2. Capture changes in an Update Set
      3. Export the Update Set as XML
      4. Replace this file with the exported XML

    Alternatively, use the ServiceNow REST API to deploy individual
    components programmatically via the catalog-items/, client-scripts/,
    server-scripts/, business-rules/, and ui-policies/ JSON definitions.
  -->
</unload>
